{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:19:51.232Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the official Claude documentation and Claude Certified Architect course materials, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Verifying & Iterating\""},{"type":"text","text":" is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"third phase of the agentic loop"},{"type":"text","text":" where Claude checks its work and decides whether to continue or finish the task."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"After taking action, Claude "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"verifies"},{"type":"text","text":" its work by re-reading files, re-running tests, or checking results, then decides whether the task is complete or needs more iterations. This is where Claude determines if it succeeded or needs to loop back to gather more context and take more action."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Activities in This Phase"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Activity"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Does"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Re-read files"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Verifies code changes were actually applied correctly"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Re-run tests"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Confirms fixes work by executing the same test that failed"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Check results"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Validates outputs (e.g., HTTP status codes, command outputs)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decision point"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Determines if task is done or needs more loop iterations"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How the Loop Works"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The complete cycle repeats until the task is done:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"gather context → take action → verify work → [repeat if needed]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each iteration is one round-trip to the Messages API:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude emits "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_use"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":" blocks"},{"type":"text","text":" and stops with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"stop_reason: \"tool_use\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Client executes the tool"},{"type":"text","text":" and appends result as "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_result"},{"type":"text","text":" block"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude sees the result"},{"type":"text","text":" and either calls another tool or produces final answer"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Loop terminates"},{"type":"text","text":" when "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"stop_reason"},{"type":"text","text":" is no longer "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_use"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"end_turn"},{"type":"text","text":")"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why It Matters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Verification is critical because:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Makes agents self-correcting"},{"type":"text","text":" — After each action, Claude sees real results (failing test, empty search, 404 error) and adapts its next step"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"A one-shot prompt can't do this"},{"type":"text","text":" — It commits to a plan before seeing any feedback"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Verification is a step, not an afterthought"},{"type":"text","text":" — Strong agents verify their own work as an explicit action inside the loop rather than trusting the first result"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Context accumulates"},{"type":"text","text":" — Every tool call and result is appended, so the window grows each turn"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Loop Properties"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Three key properties follow directly from the loop design:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Property"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Explanation"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Context accumulates"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Every tool call and result is appended; long loops need compaction or summarization"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Termination is explicit"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Loop ends when "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"stop_reason"},{"type":"text","text":" ≠ "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_use"},{"type":"text","text":", or when hitting guardrails like "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"max_turns"},{"type":"text","text":"/budget cap"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Verification is explicit"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Strong agents verify work inside the loop rather than trusting first results"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental Model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of it like a developer fixing code: after editing a file and running a test, you "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"check if it passes"},{"type":"text","text":". If it fails, you "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"loop back"},{"type":"text","text":" to understand what went wrong and try again. Claude does this autonomously through verification tool calls."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Verifying is phase 3 of the loop: gather context → take action → "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"verify"},{"type":"text","text":" → repeat until done"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The loop is your responsibility — the model never executes tools itself, only requests them"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Loop terminates when "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"stop_reason"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_use"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"end_turn"},{"type":"text","text":")"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Always bound the loop with a turn/budget cap like "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"max_turns"},{"type":"text","text":" — never assume the model will stop on its own"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Verification should be an explicit action inside the loop (re-read file, re-run test), not trust the first result"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"After each action, Claude sees real feedback and can course-correct, which is what makes it self-correcting"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The three-phase loop (gather context → take action → verify results) is what makes Claude Code an agent rather than a chatbot, enabling it to chain dozens of actions and adapt based on real feedback."}]}]}}
